  "title": "Draughtsman/Draftsman",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role and Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>To prepare Lifting Plans (Preliminary and Revision) for submission as per schedule</li><li>Apply broad idea output for calculation and visualisation</li><li>Work closely with Project Teas on drawing, amendments and updates</li><li>Identify potential operational issues and redesign plans to improve functionality</li><li>Any other adhoc duties assigned by supervisor/management</li><li><strong>Preferably with experience in AutoCAD 2023–2024</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>What We Offers:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Salary Package: Basic Salary up to $3,700 (Salary will be commensurate based on experience)</strong></li><li><strong>Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Working Incentives up to $100 per day</strong></li><li>5 Days work week</li><li>Medical/ Dental benefits</li><li>Flexible benefits</li><li>Company lunch and other staff welfares</li><li>Company Transport provided at Clementi MRT.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Ready to Join Us?</strong></p><p>Send your resume to <strong>hra@mohsengcranes.com</strong> with the subject line “Application – Draughtsman/Draftsman”. We’d love to hear how you can contribute to Moh Seng ’s next phase of growth!</p>",
